                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, E</hi> 14). I took the prisoner—he said the paper was not stolen; but a man called at the shop during his master's absence, and he bought it of him, and took it to the fishmonger's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A man came and asked me if I would buy it, there was fourteen pounds of it; I gave him 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for it, and went to sell it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good chnracter.)</p>
